                "invention-title": [
                    "Methane cracking hydrogen production device and method based on filtering combustion mode",
                    "一种基于过滤燃烧模式的甲烷裂解制氢装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a methane cracking hydrogen production device and method based on a filtering combustion mode, and belongs to the technical field of methane hydrogen production. The problems that an existing hydrogen production technology is low in efficiency and high in cost are solved. Comprising a gasification furnace body, a recovery bin, a barrier net and a tray assembly, the upper end of the gasification furnace body is provided with an outlet, the side wall of the gasification furnace body is provided with a medium inlet and an oxidant inlet, the medium inlet is located above the oxidant inlet, the barrier net is arranged in the gasification furnace body, the lower end of the gasification furnace body is connected with the recovery bin, and the recovery bin is provided with an inlet. A tray assembly is arranged in the recycling bin and corresponds to the lower end of the gasification furnace body. By utilizing the heat storage and radiation characteristics of the inert particles, the inert particles enter the recovery bin from the gasification furnace body, methane can be uniformly heated and cracked, the reaction efficiency is improved, a generated carbon black byproduct is more easily separated from the inert particles, and continuous hydrogen production is realized, so that the process for producing hydrogen through methane cracking is simplified, and the cost is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种基于过滤燃烧模式的甲烷裂解制氢装置及方法，属于甲烷制氢技术领域。解决现有制氢技术效率低，成本高的问题。包括气化炉身、回收仓、阻隔网和托盘组件，所述气化炉身的上端具有出口，气化炉身的侧壁设置有介质进口和氧化剂进口，介质进口位于氧化剂进口的上方，气化炉身内设置有阻隔网，气化炉身的下端与回收仓连接，回收仓设置有入口，回收仓内设置有托盘组件，托盘组件与气化炉身的下端对应设置。本发明利用惰性颗粒物的蓄热和辐射特性，惰性颗粒物从气化炉身进入到回收仓的，能够使甲烷受热均匀而裂解，提高反应效率，且生成的碳黑副产品更容易与惰性颗粒分离，实现连续制氢，从而简化了甲烷裂解制氢工艺，降低了成本。"
                }
            ]
